-If a committed fixture references a missing path, do not write a validator that fails only because of that known bad fixture. Instead, create a narrow follow-up task on `ppd/daemon/task-board.md` to repair the fixture reference or add the missing fixture, whichever is consistent with the already accepted fixture set.
